        "@value": "<p><span style='font-size: medium;'><strong>April 9, 2026 (10:00 AM - 8:00 PM)<br />\nApril 10, 2026 (10:00 AM - 8:00 PM)<br />\nApril 11, 2026 (9:00 AM - 7:00 PM)<br />\nApril 12, 2026 (9:00 AM - 5:00 PM)</strong><br>\nCentre de foires de Québec</span></p>\n\n<p><b>Ticket valid for one entry the day of your choice.</b></p>\n\n<p><b>Free for children 17 years old and younger.</b> (The tickets will be available only at the Centre de foires on the day of the event.)</p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
